We had the honor of working with the
extremely talented @gogon_illust, who created our new logos & brand identity for Saiko Stationery.

Gogon is known for their iconic designs; they have created beautiful works for Hololive creators like Gawr Gura, Ceres Fauna and Mori Calliope. 

As a Vtuber-owned stationery small business, we knew they would perfectly execute on our vision and bring it to life.

As expected, they created something unforgettable, cute, and cozy. 💖✨

See our latest blog post to learn more about our store mascot Mr. Sloth and our new designs! 🦥 ~ Saiko
